  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a phase II study to determine the antitumor activity of Vinorelbine and
      Cyclofosfamide association among patients with refractory tumours or in relapse with
      rhabdomyosarcomas and other soft tissue tumours, Ewing tumours, osteosarcomas, neuroblastomas
      or medulloblastomas.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
